[fn:2] The strength of relationships between two individuals is the sum of the Likert scores from questions regarding the following: feelings of trust, feelings of familiarity, confidentiality, and support.

[fn:3] This question only needs to be posed when CONTACT_OTHER is not option 9: I don't know this person yet.

[fn:4] For each game we know the type of communication (i.e. free communication over chat of video call, restricted communication through emoji's or just gameplay without interplayer communication). Also, does the game revolve around cooperation, competition or simultaneous playing without necessary interaction. And lastly, if the game does invoke interaction by design, how much interaction is needed?

